{"id":292124,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/05/维权网-各地上访维权者到日本使馆抗议被关押20余/","date":"2013-05-06T01:15:37Z","modified":"2013-05-06T01:15:37Z","title":"维权网 | 各地上访维权者到日本使馆抗议被关押20余小时（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员唐韵报道）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>日</span><span>在京的部分维权人士到日本大使馆，针对日本政府改教科书、修宪，否认历史的行径举行抗议活动时，多人被警察抓走。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>参加抗议活动的人士有江苏汤树秀，辽宁赵广军，天津冯艳春，上海吴玉芬、陈载忠，吉林王桂香，广东冉崇碧，湖北李树南等</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">19</span><span>人，大家刚到日本大使馆门前，就被麦子店派出所警察抓走，关押了</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">20</span><span>多个小时后放出。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>在麦子店派出所里，维权人士与公安警察进行针锋相对抗争。警察训斥大家：你们到这里上访是错误的。多人回答：我们是爱国之举，并不是到这里上访。南京维权人士汤树秀说：“就是找外国人我们也不会找日本人，我们与日本人有不共戴天的仇恨，这刻骨铭心的历史我们永远不会忘记。每年的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13</span><span>日</span><span>我们南京都会拉响警报，纪念南京大屠杀的死难者，以此教育我们的子孙后代勿忘国耻”。在争论不果的情况下，警察把纸笔发给大家，让写“悔过书”。汤树秀表示：“如果让我们在写悔过书和拘留上选择，我们选择拘留”。大家坚持就是不写“悔过书”，认为爱国没有错，并与警察据理力争。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">20</span><span>多个小时过去了，警方找不到维权人士爱国行动之错，于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>日</span><span>上午九点多</span><span>钟只好放人。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>江苏汤树秀</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">  </span><span>电话</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13815407808    </span><span>辽宁赵广军</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">  </span><span>电话</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">15004273556</span></div>\n<div><span>天津冯艳春</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">  </span><span>电话</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">15510931447    </span><span>上海吴玉芬</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">  </span><span>电话</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13121947938</span></div>\n<div><span>上海陈载忠</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">  </span><span>电话</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">18917038653    </span><span>吉林王桂香</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>广东冉崇碧</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">  </span><span>电话</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13240155083    </span><span>湖北李树南</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">  </span><span>电话</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13161932371</span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br /></span></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-G47gr1Lnk9Y/UYaSFnGCStI/AAAAAAAAhd0/2RFcPDU_bUo/s1600/2013-05-05+11.35.04.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-G47gr1Lnk9Y/UYaSFnGCStI/AAAAAAAAhd0/2RFcPDU_bUo/s320/2013-05-05+11.35.04.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-4HEnwgZPC2g/UYaSI1XSQoI/AAAAAAAAhd8/64_zBBY1n8I/s1600/2013-05-05+11.54.01.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-4HEnwgZPC2g/UYaSI1XSQoI/AAAAAAAAhd8/64_zBBY1n8I/s320/2013-05-05+11.54.01.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br /></span></div>\n</div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=2ea93c5b7b\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/msuvD\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],"tags":[16910,9826,19196]}